  "description": "A tranquil scene of a clear, shallow stream flowing over smooth, grey rocks. A large, reddish-brown rock dominates the foreground, partially submerged in the water. Behind it, the stream continues, bordered by lush green vegetation growing on the banks and larger, moss-covered rocks. The water is remarkably clear, allowing visibility of the rocky bed beneath. Sunlight filters through the trees, creating subtle reflections on the water's surface. The overall impression is one of natural beauty and serene stillness.",
